      <description>&lt;DIV&gt;Hey All,&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;BR&gt;We are looking to put together a helpful piece on what you should absolutely do during your first 10 days in EQ and we would like your input.&amp;nbsp; What advice would you give new players during their first 10 days?&amp;nbsp; What things do you think they should absolutely do during those first 10 days?&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Let the ideas roll!&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Thanks all.&lt;/DIV&gt;</description>
